===Format===
* '''League Stage:''''' June 20st -24th
** 24 Total teams
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 16}} teams qualify for ''Finals''
** Round-robin format.

* '''Finals:'''''  June 25st -26th
** 16 teams 
** 6 matches per day.

